message.text:
ANO DAW??? MAY ONE WEEK TRIP TO JAPAN????? ⛩️

Wait....

ANO BAYAN, AKALA KO PANAMAN TRIP TO JAPAN, ORG PALA. HAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHA 😭🫠

well... sige na nga. org muna for now, sunod nalang ang mga travels. after all, we do need to work if we want to travel all the time. tsaka, in our day and age, there's no such thing as "instant libre" baka ma-scam ka pa. if you study and calculate yung percentage na mananalo ka sa isang lottery for example, it's near impossible to win. 

kaya, I tell you, especially sa inyong mga baguhan palang o sophomores dito sa university, looking at you mga psych students here sa OPC, if you want to gain experience, lalo na to those who are interested in reviewing legal documentations, after all hindi biro biro din yung pag sa-sign ng mga contract na binabasa natin, nor any legal files that could alter and change the course of your future. or, baka ka naman interested when it comes to creating resolutions, participating in parliamentary sessions, or maybe have a voice in congress, I would recommend L&L.

kaya, right here, and right now, and this very last chance that you have today, and tonight, before 11:59pm this midnight, i'm genuinely asking you this, if you want to gain work experience, if you want to know how to scrutinize legal documents or participate in parliamentary sessions, if you want to prepare for whatever endeavours you may pursue in the future, maybe, just maybe, give us a try. You won't regret it.

If you ever wish to be part of L&L, here's the link:
🔗: https://bit.ly/FEUPsychologySociety_Membership
🔗: https://bit.ly/FEUPsychologySociety_Membership
🔗: https://bit.ly/FEUPsychologySociety_Membership

#KaPSYmaKaSaLakbay

#AscendingToGreaterHeights

message.text:
ANO DAW??? MAY ONE WEEK TRIP TO JAPAN????? ⛩️

Wait....

ANO BAYAN, AKALA KO PANAMAN TRIP TO JAPAN, ORG PALA. HAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHA 😭🫠

well... sige na nga. org muna for now, sunod nalang ang mga travels. after all, we do need to work if we want to travel all the time. tsaka, in our day and age, there's no such thing as "instant libre" baka ma-scam ka pa. if you study and calculate yung percentage na mananalo ka sa isang lottery for example, it's near impossible to win. 

kaya, I tell you, especially sa inyong mga baguhan palang o sophomores dito sa university, looking at you mga psych students here sa OPC, if you want to gain experience, lalo na to those who are interested in reviewing legal documentations, after all hindi biro biro din yung pag sa-sign ng mga contract na binabasa natin, nor any legal files that could alter and change the course of your future. or, baka ka naman interested when it comes to creating resolutions, participating in parliamentary sessions, or maybe have a voice in congress, I would recommend L&L.

kaya, right here, and right now, and this very last chance that you have today, and tonight, before 11:59pm this midnight, i'm genuinely asking you this, if you want to gain work experience, if you want to know how to scrutinize legal documents or participate in parliamentary sessions, if you want to prepare for whatever endeavours you may pursue in the future, maybe, just maybe, give us a try. You won't regret it.

If you ever wish to be part of L&L, here's the link:
🔗: https://bit.ly/FEUPsychologySociety_Membership
🔗: https://bit.ly/FEUPsychologySociety_Membership
🔗: https://bit.ly/FEUPsychologySociety_Membership
